ntry><id>d96acf11d6340ee773f77c3583ced0d6</id><title>市場永遠都係適者生存</title><updated>2025-07-22T09:05:52+08:00</updated><author><name>jaylentsui</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-22T09:05:52+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573315806"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573315806"&gt;22/7/25 HSF分析 (金天金天星閃閃)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;中位24950-25025&lt;br/&gt;向上25090-25175/ 25280-25375&lt;br/&gt;向下24885-24820/ 24765-24700&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;25樓咬住唔放, 但仍然是阻力區合埋範圍內&lt;br/&gt;先睇開市能否企好黃區, 失守24950就睇返248-247水平&lt;br/&gt;定還是小回大漲…再挑戰高位出新高?&lt;br/&gt;暫時做淡風險係較高少少, 明白25樓唔沽對唔住自己咁&lt;br/&gt;我都有咁諗,,,,但市場永遠都係適者生存&lt;br/&gt;港期唔俾跌時無謂物極必反,,,,,賭性定投機要問清楚自己&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31987914&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1132153877687ef604450108_45949172"/><published>2025-07-22T09:05:52+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>36c7d23b795377b736614638f22ae6bf</id><title>道期升；恒指開市～25050</title><updated>2025-07-22T09:33:51+08:00</updated><author><name>dwong</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-22T09:33:51+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573316060"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573316060"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;納指6連升，創歷史新高，道指升259點後倒跌，連跌2日。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;美滙指數下跌，報97.63。長債息跌至4.368厘。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;北水吸資增至70.5億元&lt;/span&gt;：受惠雅魯藏布江下游水電工程，獲資金熱炒的東方電氣，中國能源建設&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://invest.hket.com/data/HKG03996/?mtc=20048" target="_blank" uhash="2200769fd0010e7fdac8d6dc69973dca"&gt;（03996）&lt;/a&gt;及華新水泥&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://invest.hket.com/data/HKG06655/?mtc=20048" target="_blank" uhash="fc172d9e61343d1eaef198a60e134679"&gt;（06655），&lt;/a&gt;建行。沽&lt;span style="color: #ff0000; "&gt;美團 及小米。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000; "&gt;恒指上補裂口25099-25222&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000; "&gt;裂口支持24825&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000; "&gt;A股開市升，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000; "&gt;裂口支持3536&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31987933&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1132153877687ef604450108_45949172"/><published>2025-07-22T09:33:51+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>82efa954395a9029f84f69ab6e03c667</id><title>隻東方電氣尋日乜價位入，都輸撚緊㗎啦！唔明啲人仲炒乜❓</title><updated>2025-07-22T09:35:55+08:00</updated><author><name>精神裁判</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-22T09:35:55+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573316076"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573316076"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="83" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/littledd/DD_giveup.gif"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="83" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/littledd/DD_giveup.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="83" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/littledd/DD_giveup.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="83" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/littledd/DD_giveup.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="83" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/l